developers that

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:56.950
don't have the best intentions
and will use capabilities

00:07:56.950 --> 00:07:59.270
in ways that we hadn't
really anticipated.

00:07:59.270 --> 00:08:02.320
An example, by the
way, is there's

00:08:02.320 --> 00:08:04.117
different cases
where it's not really

00:08:04.117 --> 00:08:05.950
that you're trying to
do anything nefarious.

00:08:05.950 --> 00:08:08.650
