use it for other things.

00:08:31.510 --> 00:08:34.429
That's the kind of thing that
our evolving the platform.

00:08:34.429 --> 00:08:37.132
And so I think our understanding
of the world is evolving.

00:08:37.132 --> 00:08:38.590
