only, but one of the reasons

00:09:12.940 --> 00:09:14.620
why we switched to
runtime permissions

00:09:14.620 --> 00:09:17.622
is because we
realized most users,

00:09:17.622 --> 00:09:20.080
they are at the Play Store, or
they hit the Install button.

00:09:20.080 --> 00:09:21.190
And they're just going
to right away hit

00:09:21.190 --> 00:09:23.418
